dtu-sustain-setup (1.2.1-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * TPM2 Auto-Unlock now supports passphrase prompts even without an
    interactive terminal by using GUI/system prompts and secure keyfile flow.
  * Added a completion popup after "Run All Admin Modules" that asks whether
    the machine should reboot now.

 -- DTU Sustain IT <support@sustain.dtu.dk>  Tue, 07 Jul 2026 12:30:00 +0200

dtu-sustain-setup (1.2.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Added an "Update to latest version" button in the app header.
  * The button downloads the latest GitHub release, removes the old
    installation, and reinstalls the new version.
  * FollowMe printers now use the local Konica C751i PPD with explicit
    queue defaults.

