dtu-sustain-setup (1.1.3-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Domain join scripts now ignore DTU_HOSTNAME when the DTU Sustain
    profile is selected, so the existing hostname is kept unchanged.

 -- DTU Sustain IT <support@sustain.dtu.dk>  Tue, 07 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200

dtu-sustain-setup (1.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Dynamic department selection: load_site_conf() now sources
    /etc/dtu-setup/dtu-<dept>.env when DTU_DEPARTMENT is set,
    falling back to site.conf for backward compatibility.
  * GUI auto-detects DTU_DEPARTMENT from /etc/dtu-setup/site.conf
    on startup and syncs the department dropdown accordingly.

 -- DTU Sustain IT <support@sustain.dtu.dk>  Tue, 01 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200

